introduction silverglow asset pty ltd (silverglow or the company), the defendant corporation, was incorporated on 11 april 2005 for the specific purpose of purchasing land near geraldton, western australia and undertaking the sunset beach residential subdivision development.
the plaintiffs are shareholders in silverglow.
